{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/gatsby로-github-blog-만들기-3/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>한글날이 있길래, 월요일 연차를 붙여 썼다. AI 이노베이션 강의 내용 복습하고 시간이 남아서 블로그를 업데이트 해보았다.</p>\n<p>어느 덧 블로그 시작한지 1달이 다 됐다. 깃허브 블로그 쓰다 보니까 수학 수식이나 프로그래밍 코드가 안 이쁘게 보여서 (...) 구글링을 통해 보완책을 마련해 봤다.</p>\n<p>이 두 개의 plugin 모두 gatsby-transformer-remark 하위에 추가하면 된다.</p>\n<p>메모  </p>\n<ul>\n<li>math > <a href=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.com/plugins/gatsby-remark-mathjax/\">https://www.gatsbyjs.com/plugins/gatsby-remark-mathjax/</a>  </li>\n<li>code > <a href=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.com/plugins/gatsby-remark-prismjs/\">https://www.gatsbyjs.com/plugins/gatsby-remark-prismjs/</a>  </li>\n<li>prismjs thema > <a href=\"https://github.com/PrismJS/prism/tree/1d5047df37aacc900f8270b1c6215028f6988eb1/themes\">https://github.com/PrismJS/prism/tree/1d5047df37aacc900f8270b1c6215028f6988eb1/themes</a>  </li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"깃허브로-블로그-만들기---3\" style=\"position:relative;\">깃허브로 블로그 만들기 - 3<a href=\"#%EA%B9%83%ED%97%88%EB%B8%8C%EB%A1%9C-%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8-%EB%A7%8C%EB%93%A4%EA%B8%B0---3\" aria-label=\"깃허브로 블로그 만들기   3 permalink\" class=\"custom-class after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n<h3 id=\"1-mathjax-적용-방법-with-helmet\" style=\"position:relative;\">(1) mathjax 적용 방법 (with Helmet)<a href=\"#1-mathjax-%EC%A0%81%EC%9A%A9-%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95-with-helmet\" aria-label=\"1 mathjax 적용 방법 with helmet permalink\" class=\"custom-class after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n<ol>\n<li>gatsby-remark-mathjax 설치  </li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-shell line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-shell\">$ <span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> --save gatsby-transformer-remark gatsby-remark-mathjax</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>gatsby-config.js 파일 수정  </li>\n</ol>\n<p>기존의 gatsby-transformer-remark 에 추가하지 않고, 새로 만들었다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-text line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-text\">module.exports = {\n  plugins: [\n    {\n      resolve: `gatsby-transformer-remark`,\n      options: {\n        plugins: [\n          `gatsby-remark-mathjax`,\n        ],\n      },\n    },\n  ],\n}</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>blog post 관련 template 수정 (with Helmet)</li>\n</ol>\n<p>내 경우 /src/templates/blog-post.js 를 사용 중이어서 이 파일을 수정했다.<br>\nscript 추가할 방법을 찾다가 Helmet 안에 그냥 집어 넣었다.  </p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-bash line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> helmet --save</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-js line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token comment\">// 위 쪽에 추가하고</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> Helmet <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"react-helmet\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 이 아래는 return 내 본문 쪽 부분에 추가한다.</span>\n\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Helmet<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>script<span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token string\">\"MathJax = {tex: {inlineMath: [['$', '$']]}}\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>script<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>script\n      id<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"MathJax-script\"</span>\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">async</span>\n      src<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mathjax@3/es5/tex-mml-chtml.js\"</span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>script<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>Helmet<span class=\"token operator\">></span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>내 경우 post 부분이 이래서 <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;/Box&gt;</code> 위에 script를 이 안에 집어 넣었다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-javascript line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Box\n  dangerouslySetInnerHTML<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> __html<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> post<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>html <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  css<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> lineHeight<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'30px'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> position<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'static'</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>Box<span class=\"token operator\">></span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>위 코드를 추가하면, (블로그 게시물) 마크다운 파일에 적용된다.</p>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"2-prismjs-추가\" style=\"position:relative;\">(2) prismjs 추가<a href=\"#2-prismjs-%EC%B6%94%EA%B0%80\" aria-label=\"2 prismjs 추가 permalink\" class=\"custom-class after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n<ol>\n<li>gatsby-remark-prismjs 설치  </li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-bash line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> --save gatsby-transformer-remark gatsby-remark-prismjs prismjs</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>gatsby-config.js 파일 수정  </li>\n</ol>\n<p>아래 내용을 굳이 다 안 써도 된다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-javascript line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">  plugins<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      resolve<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">gatsby-transformer-remark</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      options<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        plugins<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n          <span class=\"token comment\">// 20201012 programming code</span>\n          <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">gatsby-remark-mathjax</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\n          <span class=\"token comment\">// 20201012 mathematical expression</span>\n          <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n            resolve<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">gatsby-remark-prismjs</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n            options<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n              <span class=\"token comment\">// Class prefix for &lt;pre> tags containing syntax highlighting;</span>\n              <span class=\"token comment\">// defaults to 'language-' (e.g. &lt;pre class=\"language-js\">).</span>\n              <span class=\"token comment\">// If your site loads Prism into the browser at runtime,</span>\n              <span class=\"token comment\">// (e.g. for use with libraries like react-live),</span>\n              <span class=\"token comment\">// you may use this to prevent Prism from re-processing syntax.</span>\n              <span class=\"token comment\">// This is an uncommon use-case though;</span>\n              <span class=\"token comment\">// If you're unsure, it's best to use the default value.</span>\n              classPrefix<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"language-\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n              <span class=\"token comment\">// This is used to allow setting a language for inline code</span>\n              <span class=\"token comment\">// (i.e. single backticks) by creating a separator.</span>\n              <span class=\"token comment\">// This separator is a string and will do no white-space</span>\n              <span class=\"token comment\">// stripping.</span>\n              <span class=\"token comment\">// A suggested value for English speakers is the non-ascii</span>\n              <span class=\"token comment\">// character '›'.</span>\n              inlineCodeMarker<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">null</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n              <span class=\"token comment\">// This lets you set up language aliases.  For example,</span>\n              <span class=\"token comment\">// setting this to '{ sh: \"bash\" }' will let you use</span>\n              <span class=\"token comment\">// the language \"sh\" which will highlight using the</span>\n              <span class=\"token comment\">// bash highlighter.</span>\n              aliases<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n              <span class=\"token comment\">// This toggles the display of line numbers globally alongside the code.</span>\n              <span class=\"token comment\">// To use it, add the following line in gatsby-browser.js</span>\n              <span class=\"token comment\">// right after importing the prism color scheme:</span>\n              <span class=\"token comment\">//  require(\"prismjs/plugins/line-numbers/prism-line-numbers.css\")</span>\n              <span class=\"token comment\">// Defaults to false.</span>\n              <span class=\"token comment\">// If you wish to only show line numbers on certain code blocks,</span>\n              <span class=\"token comment\">// leave false and use the {numberLines: true} syntax below</span>\n              showLineNumbers<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n              <span class=\"token comment\">// If setting this to true, the parser won't handle and highlight inline</span>\n              <span class=\"token comment\">// code used in markdown i.e. single backtick code like `this`.</span>\n              noInlineHighlight<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n              <span class=\"token comment\">// This adds a new language definition to Prism or extend an already</span>\n              <span class=\"token comment\">// existing language definition. More details on this option can be</span>\n              <span class=\"token comment\">// found under the header \"Add new language definition or extend an</span>\n              <span class=\"token comment\">// existing language\" below.</span>\n              languageExtensions<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n                <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n                  language<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"superscript\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n                  extend<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"javascript\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n                  definition<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n                    superscript_types<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token regex\"><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-source language-regex\">(SuperType)</span><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n                  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n                  insertBefore<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n                    <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n                      superscript_keywords<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token regex\"><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-source language-regex\">(superif|superelse)</span><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n                    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n                  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n                <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n              <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n              <span class=\"token comment\">// Customize the prompt used in shell output</span>\n              <span class=\"token comment\">// Values below are default</span>\n              prompt<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n                user<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"root\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n                host<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"localhost\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n                global<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n              <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n              <span class=\"token comment\">// By default the HTML entities &lt;>&amp;'\" are escaped.</span>\n              <span class=\"token comment\">// Add additional HTML escapes by providing a mapping</span>\n              <span class=\"token comment\">// of HTML entities and their escape value IE: { '}': '&amp;#123;' }</span>\n              escapeEntities<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n            <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n          <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>gatsby-browser.js 에 추가</li>\n</ol>\n<p>src 디렉토리 상위 경로에 gatsby-browser.js 파일을 생성하고, 아래 내용을 입력한다. (내 경우 puttylike.github.io 디렉토리였다.)  </p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-js line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"prismjs/themes/prism-okaidia.css\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>여기까지하면 기본적인 세팅이 완료된다.</p>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>기타 option</li>\n</ol>\n<p>위의 prism-okaidia.css 말고 다른 파일을 쓰고 싶다면, 여기 <a href=\"https://github.com/PrismJS/prism/tree/1d5047df37aacc900f8270b1c6215028f6988eb1/themes\">링크</a>에 있는 다른 css 파일을 쓸 수도 있고, 직접 css 파일을 만들어 import하는 경우도 있겠다.</p>\n<p>나머지 내용은 공식 문서 <a href=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.com/plugins/gatsby-remark-prismjs/\">링크</a>를 참고하면 될 듯 싶다.</p>\n<p>위 링크에 있는 내용이다만, 소스 코드 옆에 line numbering을 하고 싶다면, gatsby-browser.js 에 아래 내용을 추가하면 된다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-js line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"prismjs/plugins/line-numbers/prism-line-numbers.css\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// Add line numbering</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"3-수식--코드-작성-방법\" style=\"position:relative;\">(3) 수식 &#x26; 코드 작성 방법<a href=\"#3-%EC%88%98%EC%8B%9D--%EC%BD%94%EB%93%9C-%EC%9E%91%EC%84%B1-%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95\" aria-label=\"3 수식  코드 작성 방법 permalink\" class=\"custom-class after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n<ol>\n<li>수학 수식 작성하기</li>\n</ol>\n<p>수식 앞뒤로 <code class=\"language-text\">$$</code> 또는 <code class=\"language-text\">$</code> 를 감싸면 된다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-text line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-text\">$$f(x) = 1/(1+e^x)$$  \n$g(x) = x^3+2x+c$  </code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>$f(x) = 1/(1+e^x)$<br>\n$g(x) = x^3+2x+c$  </p>\n<p>한번씩 로딩이 뭔가 제때 안 되는 느낌적인 느낌(?)이 드는데, 일단 되니까 이대로 마무리지었다.</p>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>코드 작성하기</li>\n</ol>\n<p>```javascript 과 ``` 사이에 소스 코드를 넣으면 된다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-javascript line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">plugins<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    resolve<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">gatsby-transformer-remark</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    options<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      plugins<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n        <span class=\"token comment\">// 20201012 programming code</span>\n        <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">gatsby-remark-mathjax</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token comment\">// 20201012 mathematical expression</span>\n        <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">gatsby-remark-prismjs</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<hr>\n<h4 id=\"-참고할-만한-웹사이트\" style=\"position:relative;\">** 참고할 만한 웹사이트<a href=\"#-%EC%B0%B8%EA%B3%A0%ED%95%A0-%EB%A7%8C%ED%95%9C-%EC%9B%B9%EC%82%AC%EC%9D%B4%ED%8A%B8\" aria-label=\" 참고할 만한 웹사이트 permalink\" class=\"custom-class after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h4>\n<p>gatsby... 그니까 react에서 mathjax가 잘 안 된다는 글들이 좀 보인다.</p>\n<p>대안으로는 katex나 react-mathjax 등이 있다고 하는데, 나는 해결이 돼 그냥 링크 목록만 올린다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://zhoumingjun.github.io/post/2018-09-04-enable-mathjax-in-gatsby/\">https://zhoumingjun.github.io/post/2018-09-04-enable-mathjax-in-gatsby/</a>  </li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/gatsbyjs/gatsby/issues/16983\">https://github.com/gatsbyjs/gatsby/issues/16983</a>  </li>\n<li><a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/59384306/how-to-add-katex-plugin-into-gatsby-theme-blog\">https://stackoverflow.com/questions/59384306/how-to-add-katex-plugin-into-gatsby-theme-blog</a>  </li>\n<li><a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/45106453/rendering-math-in-react-component\">https://stackoverflow.com/questions/45106453/rendering-math-in-react-component</a>  </li>\n</ul>\n<p>그리고 prismjs 관련해서 볼 만한 게시물은 다음과 같다. <strong>혹시 적용 안 되면, gatsby-browser.js 파일 위치가 맞는지 확인할 것.</strong> 내가 이거로 삽질했다. (...)</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://niklasmtj.de/blog/prismjs-in-gatsbyjs\">https://niklasmtj.de/blog/prismjs-in-gatsbyjs</a>  </li>\n<li><a href=\"https://prince.dev/prism-react-renderer\">https://prince.dev/prism-react-renderer</a>  </li>\n<li><a href=\"https://prismjs.com/\">https://prismjs.com/</a></li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h4 id=\"-개선하고-싶은-부분\" style=\"position:relative;\">** 개선하고 싶은 부분<a href=\"#-%EA%B0%9C%EC%84%A0%ED%95%98%EA%B3%A0-%EC%8B%B6%EC%9D%80-%EB%B6%80%EB%B6%84\" aria-label=\" 개선하고 싶은 부분 permalink\" class=\"custom-class after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h4>\n<ul>\n<li>블로그 관련  </li>\n</ul>\n<p>카테고리(메뉴)나 태그로 글 모아보기 기능, 댓글달기 기능을 이건 대체 언제 하지? ㅎ...  그리고 댓글 쓰기나 (Github 연결? Disqus?) 블로거 소개 좀 붙이고 싶다. 또한, 소스 코드 정리를 좀 하고 싶은데... 엄두가 안 난다.</p>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/gatsby%EB%A1%9C-github-blog-%EB%A7%8C%EB%93%A4%EA%B8%B0-3/#%EA%B9%83%ED%97%88%EB%B8%8C%EB%A1%9C-%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8-%EB%A7%8C%EB%93%A4%EA%B8%B0---3\">깃허브로 블로그 만들기 - 3</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/gatsby%EB%A1%9C-github-blog-%EB%A7%8C%EB%93%A4%EA%B8%B0-3/#1-mathjax-%EC%A0%81%EC%9A%A9-%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95-with-helmet\">(1) mathjax 적용 방법 (with Helmet)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/gatsby%EB%A1%9C-github-blog-%EB%A7%8C%EB%93%A4%EA%B8%B0-3/#2-prismjs-%EC%B6%94%EA%B0%80\">(2) prismjs 추가</a></li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/gatsby%EB%A1%9C-github-blog-%EB%A7%8C%EB%93%A4%EA%B8%B0-3/#3-%EC%88%98%EC%8B%9D--%EC%BD%94%EB%93%9C-%EC%9E%91%EC%84%B1-%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95\">(3) 수식 &#x26; 코드 작성 방법</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/gatsby%EB%A1%9C-github-blog-%EB%A7%8C%EB%93%A4%EA%B8%B0-3/#-%EC%B0%B8%EA%B3%A0%ED%95%A0-%EB%A7%8C%ED%95%9C-%EC%9B%B9%EC%82%AC%EC%9D%B4%ED%8A%B8\">** 참고할 만한 웹사이트</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/gatsby%EB%A1%9C-github-blog-%EB%A7%8C%EB%93%A4%EA%B8%B0-3/#-%EA%B0%9C%EC%84%A0%ED%95%98%EA%B3%A0-%EC%8B%B6%EC%9D%80-%EB%B6%80%EB%B6%84\">** 개선하고 싶은 부분</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"Github Blog 만들기3 - 수식, 코드 스타일 추가 (by gatsby)"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/gatsby로-github-blog-만들기-3/"}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}